I am so confused right now.... i feel like i have done something wrong.... i have a new boyfriend and we have been dating for a nmonth as of the 6th. And i feel great i really like him and he is good to me. he trats me right and he isn't like the other asses that i have dated.  We hadd a fight tonight, and i am not even sure what started it.... To recap the last few weeks. my boyfriend lent his game cube to my brother ( I know stupid thing to do) but then JAmes took it amd he sold it to cash converters. When my boyfriend found out he was furious which is understandable.  And he wants his money from JAmes for the Game.. Well I agree. But what he doesn't realize is that he is never going to get the money from James. There is no way that James has 300 dollars to replace the system and games and wireless controllers or whatever it is. And he has been going on about it ever since he found out. So the other night i told him that I didn't want to hear any more about it at all. ANd he agreed.
    So you would figure that it would be over.  Well this after noon Cher  decided to tease him and tell hiom that she accidently broke his D.S game thingy. Well he got a little mad about it. I thought that it was no big  deal she was havign a little bit of fun.  Then today i started picking on him, and anyone who knows me knows that i say whatever is on my mind i don't ever think before i speak. SO tonight he got mad at me and he yelled at me and told me that it wasn't a good idea to have him pissed at me. LIke what the hell. I was joking if oyu can't take a joke. I am sorry. But i never have thought before i spoke. And most  of the shit i say i don't even remember what i did say after it came out of my mouth. I can say something to you and not even realize that i said it. . I am just aa little annou=yed right now.  It makes me so angry when people take the things that i say so seriously. like yes threre are some things that i want to  be taken seriously but most of the time i am just joking.

       Then there is the fact that a certain person has had some problems over the last few weeks (I am not revealing an ideantity for their own sake) and i have not had a problem with it. But my god  certain people need to hink before they speak on things they say to this person especially when they are in hte state they are ion. you need to think how what you say will impact people. Now i know i sound like a hugh hipocrit, and i am but you need to understand the situation. and if either of these peole ever read this then i hope they understand what i mean. i am njot angry at either person least of all the person  with the problem. I love you. you were put in my life for a reason. and you are not going anywhere.

    Alright now that i have rambled on and on and on. i am getting ready  for bed i love yas and will talk more later byes

But besides that she has had to know about my problem and she won't do anything about it. And I am scared. I always knew that there was something wrong but I never figured it was as bad as it is. All I will say is that I have over 36 scars and I have about 6 rips that make it painful for me to do certain things. ANd it is all thanks to my fucking father. I hate him. I wish that I could have him killed he ruined my life and I will never be the same again. He destroyed me and I can never get away from what he did. I feel so empty inside and I feel like I am broken and can never be fixed. I have spent many hours crying over this and I don't know what to do . I know that I have to see a doctor  but I am scared to go because I don't think they can do anytrhing except maybe reconstructive surgery but then I don't want surgery. ANd I am terrified.
